{"tid":1376550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"若支持港鐵罷工, 一般市民何不「先集結, 後癱瘓」","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T22:59:33.000Z","uid":21699,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e883b89928cc74089991fa866114bb009dd2f8c9","tid":1376550,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"1. 鐵路全線失效, 全港交通阻塞, 人們想返工也不能返, 實為「罷工」的終極催化劑<br />\n2. 車長想罷工<br />\n3. 市民主動癱瘓鐵路可減輕車長罷工壓力, 令鐵路癱瘓+車長罷工 更容易發生<br />\n4. 但早前「癱瘓鐵路」行動一直缺少成效, 何故？因為一兩個人唔成事, 群眾見你阻住架車開出就屌爆你<br />\n5. 所以, 何不仿傚遊行, 人多才安全, 「先集結, 後癱瘓」, 令每個人都可以無代價癱瘓鐵路?<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n七月３０號，朝早點九龍塘集結，一齊搵個藉口癱瘓鐵路全線"},{"pid":"409ac48aaf12ff5b120d8904b562e8adf466af61","tid":1376550,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323decefcd0a0398463be569f69b035939c2dea9","tid":1376550,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d350be641a0096693cc20bf46c4125c0e0dd9dd6","tid":1376550,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:02:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 但早前「癱瘓鐵路」行動一直缺少成效, 何故？因為一兩個人唔成事, 群眾見你阻住架車開出就屌爆你<br />\n5. 所以, 何不仿傚遊行, 人多才安全, 「先集結, 後癱瘓」, 令每個人都可以無代價癱瘓鐵路?<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ec7c7827c12dc3d20d92dcf4eb68297d13fc476f","tid":1376550,"uid":256914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"每條線同時間阻幾班 就成功 <br />\n推"},{"pid":"7278faa82f106e2cec1b958cffa5ebfc4f01c352","tid":1376550,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:04:20.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"8c8fd90d2eacae6b9bb6e0b41e1ed3d6c7833c1e","tid":1376550,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28